      <title>冲突加剧，刚果出现“前所未有”的人道主义危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/-unprecedented-humanitarian-crisis-in-congo-as-conflict-rages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国驻刚果民主共和国维和特派团团长告诉安理会，刚果民主共和国矿产资源丰富的东部省份战事愈演愈烈，一场人道主义灾难正在该国上演。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/-unprecedented-humanitarian-crisis-in-congo-as-conflict-rages</guid>
